{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 68,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 52,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5272,
        "text": "Nun. By the Pen and the (Record) which (men) write,-",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5273,
        "text": "Thou art not, by the Grace of thy Lord, mad or possessed.",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5274,
        "text": "Nay, verily for thee is a Reward unfailing:",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5275,
        "text": "And thou (standest) on an exalted standard of character.",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5276,
        "text": "Soon wilt thou see, and they will see,",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5277,
        "text": "Which of you is afflicted with madness.",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5278,
        "text": "Verily it is thy Lord that knoweth best, which (among men) hath strayed from His Path: and He knoweth best those who receive (true) Guidance.",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5279,
        "text": "So hearken not to those who deny (the Truth).",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5280,
        "text": "Their desire is that thou shouldst be pliant: so would they be pliant.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5281,
        "text": "Heed not the type of despicable men,- ready with oaths,",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5282,
        "text": "A slanderer, going about with calumnies,",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5283,
        "text": "(Habitually) hindering (all) good, transgressing beyond bounds, deep in sin,",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5284,
        "text": "Violent (and cruel),- with all that, base-born,-",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5285,
        "text": "Because he possesses wealth and (numerous) sons.",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5286,
        "text": "When to him are rehearsed Our Signs, \"Tales of the ancients\", he cries!",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5287,
        "text": "Soon shall We brand (the beast) on the snout!",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5288,
        "text": "Verily We have tried them as We tried the People of the Garden, when they resolved to gather the fruits of the (garden) in the morning.",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5289,
        "text": "But made no reservation, (\"If it be Allah's Will\").",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5290,
        "text": "Then there came on the (garden) a visitation from thy Lord, (which swept away) all around, while they were asleep.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5291,
        "text": "So the (garden) became, by the morning, like a dark and desolate spot, (whose fruit had been gathered).",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5292,
        "text": "As the morning broke, they called out, one to another,-",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5293,
        "text": "\"Go ye to your tilth (betimes) in the morning, if ye would gather the fruits.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5294,
        "text": "So they departed, conversing in secret low tones, (saying)-",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5295,
        "text": "\"Let not a single indigent person break in upon you into the (garden) this day.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5296,
        "text": "And they opened the morning, strong in an (unjust) resolve.",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5297,
        "text": "But when they saw the (garden), they said: \"We have surely lost our way:",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5298,
        "text": "\"Indeed we are shut out (of the fruits of our labour)!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5299,
        "text": "Said one of them, more just (than the rest): \"Did I not say to you, 'Why not glorify (Allah)?'\"",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5300,
        "text": "They said: \"Glory to our Lord! Verily we have been doing wrong!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5301,
        "text": "Then they turned, one against another, in reproach.",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5302,
        "text": "They said: \"Alas for us! We have indeed transgressed!",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5303,
        "text": "\"It may be that our Lord will give us in exchange a better (garden) than this: for we do turn to Him (in repentance)!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5304,
        "text": "Such is the Punishment (in this life); but greater is the Punishment in the Hereafter,- if only they knew!",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5305,
        "text": "Verily, for the Righteous, are Gardens of Delight, in the Presence of their Lord.",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5306,
        "text": "Shall We then treat the People of Faith like the People of Sin?",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5307,
        "text": "What is the matter with you? How judge ye?",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5308,
        "text": "Or have ye a book through which ye learn-",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5309,
        "text": "That ye shall have, through it whatever ye choose?",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5310,
        "text": "Or have ye Covenants with Us to oath, reaching to the Day of Judgment, (providing) that ye shall have whatever ye shall demand?",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5311,
        "text": "Ask thou of them, which of them will stand surety for that!",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5312,
        "text": "Or have they some \"Partners\" (in Allahhead)? Then let them produce their \"partners\", if they are truthful!",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5313,
        "text": "The Day that the shin shall be laid bare, and they shall be summoned to bow in adoration, but they shall not be able,-",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5314,
        "text": "Their eyes will be cast down,- ignominy will cover them; seeing that they had been summoned aforetime to bow in adoration, while they were whole, (and had refused).",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5315,
        "text": "Then leave Me alone with such as reject this Message: by degrees shall We punish them from directions they perceive not.",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5316,
        "text": "A (long) respite will I grant them: truly powerful is My Plan.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5317,
        "text": "Or is it that thou dost ask them for a reward, so that they are burdened with a load of debt?-",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5318,
        "text": "Or that the Unseen is in their hands, so that they can write it down?",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5319,
        "text": "So wait with patience for the Command of thy Lord, and be not like the Companion of the Fish,- when he cried out in agony.",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5320,
        "text": "Had not Grace from his Lord reached him, he would indeed have been cast off on the naked shore, in disgrace.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5321,
        "text": "Thus did his Lord choose him and make him of the Company of the Righteous.",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5322,
        "text": "And the Unbelievers would almost trip thee up with their eyes when they hear the Message; and they say: \"Surely he is possessed!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5323,
        "text": "But it is nothing less than a Message to all the worlds.",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
